high_descs: move forwards to the kitchen counter ahead, then turn left and face the kitchen sink
grab a fork out of the right side sink there
move to the left just a bit and face the kitchen sink again
place the fork on a plate inside of the cabinet below the left side kitchen sink
pick up the plate with the fork on it and close the cabinet door
turn around to back up just a bit and then face the kitchen sink again

high_descs: Walk forwards to the microwave then turn left to face the kitchen sink.
Pick up the fork that is inside the sink.
Turn left then turn right towards the adjacent sink.
Open the brown cabinet underneath the sink and place the fork on top of the plate.
Pick up the plate from inside the cabinet.
Close the cabinet door and face the sink.
Place the plate with the fork on top inside the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the fork and plate inside the kitchen sink.

high_descs: Walk towards the microwave, then hang a left and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the metal fork out of the right sink basin.
Turn left and walk towards the counter, then turn right to face the sink.
Open the cabinet door directly below the leftmost sink basin and put the fork on the plate that is inside.
Pick up the plate with the fork on it out of the cabinet below the sink and close the cabinet.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn back around to face the sink.
Put the plate with the fork on it in the leftmost sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a fork on it in the sink.
